Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.80,0:01:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,永别了  涅吉小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.38,0:01:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,超同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.81,0:01:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再会了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:42.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  总有一天还会见面！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}学园祭结束
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.01,0:02:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有就是…古奈尔先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.53,0:02:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之所以今天会来找你  是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.21,0:02:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  他现在还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.19,0:02:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「英国」指的就是回威尔士之事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.44,0:02:26.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那里有通往魔法世界的大门
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:30.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:33.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定回威尔士…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或许…这一去就不回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.43,0:02:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}然后  放暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.82,0:02:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不允许你就这么一去不回
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:46.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向我保证你一定会回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.50,0:02:49.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你身为我们班主任的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.97,0:02:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个社团就是大家为了和你一起找到父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:57.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,并且确保你能平安回到学园而成立的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.05,0:03:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,名誉顾问？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.52,0:03:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当初我是没有回绝过你们啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.61,0:03:05.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当真想把我的别墅当作活动室吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.76,0:03:13.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好咧  大家加油修行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}大家的修行开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:21.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害  真的倒下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.39,0:03:23.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  这样一来我也会超能力啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太完美了  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.21,0:03:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好！  既然如此  我们一决胜负吧  古菲！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好！  随时奉陪！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.59,0:03:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Imperium Graphices Inferno Aniki{\r}\N落书帝国  炎之魔人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虎形拳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.02,0:03:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小刹  快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  小刹你受伤了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.63,0:03:49.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  我的道具只能治疗3分钟以内的伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:53.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我真没用  对不起啦  小刹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:57.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或许舔一下就能治好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:04.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐…你居然…！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.29,0:04:10.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  已经完成78小时的学习了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.69,0:04:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.72,0:04:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:14.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩真不简单…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  接下来就由我来教授你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.28,0:04:18.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.65,0:04:27.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼…拿走！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.01,0:04:37.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,连续7天  我已经坚持下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你还有什么话说？
