Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,身为同伴  为什么不再装扮得更奇幻一点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去！  男子校服可是我的战斗服！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.21,0:07:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我作为顾问而…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.42,0:07:42.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我啥时候成为她们的伙伴啦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.86,0:07:46.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪  千雨不是我们的同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.97,0:07:48.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.56,0:07:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…现有成员还真是壮观啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.14,0:07:56.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里  好戏还在后头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.34,0:08:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的道具也是越磨练越博大精深
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞  修行万岁！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人家还想不断提升能力呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:09.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是群悠闲的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.16,0:08:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到这帮人是我的伙伴…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.11,0:08:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的头疼就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  伙伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  慢着  才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:19.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我啥时候成为她们的伙伴啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.96,0:08:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.26,0:08:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  小家伙们都高兴得不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.64,0:08:28.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样  大家能如此积极让我非常欣慰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:30.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候出发？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.85,0:08:32.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,预订为8月12日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有两个多礼拜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过充其量也就是在首都转转吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  再远的话…也只能去逛逛附近的观光地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.56,0:08:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没指望光靠这个暑假就能查明父亲的行踪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过嘛  你们就当作观光去领略一下魔法国度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.86,0:08:56.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好～  大家想去英国吗！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:57.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.29,0:08:59.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何都想去！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.57,0:09:00.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快完成修行  向威尔士进发！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:07.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一群白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:11.40,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}「要前往何处呢？吉尔…」…出自结婚塔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:11.40,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}「期待第四（回）？！」这次OAD预计只有三集…贴这纸条的意思又是要看DVD销量吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:14.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听到啰  听到啰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大新闻到手！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唰～  撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:22.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枫姐亲传  隐秘逃脱术
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:29.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让你久等了  明日菜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是调查结果
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:33.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还好啦  我没等多久
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.73,0:09:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,效率挺高的嘛  班长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪广财团一出手  这种程度的调查简直易如反掌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.80,0:09:44.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,况且  这不是因为你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.59,0:09:46.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…而是为了涅吉老师而做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:47.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好好…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:49.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,于是  到底怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…看来涅吉老师的父亲纳吉·斯普林菲尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.37,0:09:58.90,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,除雪广绫香外禁止阅览  关于纳吉·斯普林菲尔德的第一次调查报告书\N雪广财团国际情报部门  综合情报分析部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,的确在10年前就已经下落不明了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他并没有去世呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不清楚  总之目前下落不明…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个世界下落不明…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说  最终还是在魔法世界里啰…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.49,0:10:12.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:15.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是能找到的最全的文本资料了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果要继续深入调查的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,需要花费大量人员和时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.94,0:10:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  如果为了涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全世界万人规模的调查我也在所不辞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.00,0:10:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  慢着慢着  不用做到那一步啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经有线索了  暂时就免了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.62,0:10:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:35.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢啦  班长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了你  我们离涅吉的父亲又近了许多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.48,0:10:40.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:47.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.94,0:10:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜你这叛徒！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.72,0:10:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎…什么意思嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:54.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟什么事  莳绘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,班长你给我评评理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:10:59.61,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}请稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.85,0:11:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你  你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.73,0:11:04.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了寻找涅吉老师的父亲而组建了新社团
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞒着我们卿卿我我远赴英国举办合宿旅行！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有…我们并没有故意瞒着你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.95,0:11:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,更谈不上卿卿我我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.51,0:11:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用不着解释
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.87,0:11:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好你个明日菜…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一方面骗我给你提供情报…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.75,0:11:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…这种重大活动反而要瞒着我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,书店妹妹和春春也会一起去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.44,0:11:27.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然将我们排除在外
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.23,0:11:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜你这坏女人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.43,0:11:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想去！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:30.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,的确  新社团会举办合宿旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.64,0:11:38.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但尽管去的是英国  同时还得去些特殊的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.37,0:11:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为…为此我们从学园祭开始就一直特训到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.92,0:11:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特殊？  要去山上吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.86,0:11:49.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是啊是啊  有攀岩什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不能带没有接受过训练的人去…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.60,0:11:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.76,0:11:57.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种烂理由谁信啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还我！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.83,0:12:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…班长？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.38,0:12:06.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还我  还我  还我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  好慢！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.11,0:12:09.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好快！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:11.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莳绘同学  鸣泷姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住那个坏女人！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.03,0:12:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接招  明日菜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.73,0:12:20.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好耶  抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.95,0:12:27.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.94,0:12:28.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住她！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:45.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  班长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.14,0:12:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以后一定会向你道谢的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.16,0:12:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜同学  什么时候这么厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:12:58.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,狼狈不狼狈啊  班长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.06,0:13:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,依…依文洁琳同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:01.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,依文
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新社团…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.27,0:13:05.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,名誉顾问！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.11,0:13:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也给你们一个试试本领的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:09.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟我们是同学嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你们在闹些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.66,0:13:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.79,0:13:17.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天正好是夏日祭典啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定能去英国旅行的新社团！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘  裕奈你小声点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.03,0:13:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么有趣的活动胆敢瞒着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.38,0:13:34.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可饶恕喵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:37.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果通过了依文给出的入团测验
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.16,0:13:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们应该也能去英国吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:40.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.22,0:13:45.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那些新社团的成员待会貌似会去参加夏日祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新社团的全体成员都会佩戴这种别针徽章
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.04,0:13:53.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁抢到它  我就追加批准她入部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:58.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,纳吉先生说不定会出现在涅吉的故乡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.03,0:14:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…裕奈  不是这么回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.29,0:14:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看准时机夺取徽章  听起来并不难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:08.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛  也不是那么简单的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.51,0:14:08.98,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,英国文化研究社团  涅吉魔社（暂定）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.39,0:14:12.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这些成员是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.36,0:14:15.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,长濑同学  樱咲同学  古菲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻帆良武道会的猛将们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.07,0:14:20.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她们身上似乎完全没有可乘之机…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:24.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且明日菜也很强…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:25.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,五月不穿浴衣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.77,0:14:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我要回店里一趟…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:28.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是古菲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:30.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说曹操…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那谁就到啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:34.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,的确戴着白色徽章呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.36,0:14:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但对手可是小古啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:39.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,图书馆的两位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.99,0:14:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  这个徽章究竟是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道  社团成员的标志吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.93,0:14:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是咱们的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但…但是  对最温和的两位下手会不会太卑鄙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.94,0:15:00.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,攻其弱点乃兵法之本
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.47,0:15:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了确保英国之旅…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.48,0:15:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…这也是没办法的办法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.06,0:15:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玩具枪从哪来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:09.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小家败气的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.29,0:15:10.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你该称赞我行事谨慎才对！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:11.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祭典真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.38,0:15:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和学园祭的氛围又有所不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,噢  涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是捞金鱼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.16,0:15:25.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要来比一比
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.39,0:15:34.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到还能跟小刹一起参加祭典呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:36.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那两位关系也很亲密呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.59,0:15:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,茶茶丸同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.70,0:15:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,徽章？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在分发给部里的每一个成员…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:51.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是主人送给各位的特别礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.41,0:15:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀～这是什么？  好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.54,0:15:55.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以收下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:15:58.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个徽章就是社团成员的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:16:01.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,希望大家能佩戴好出席今晚的祭典…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.78,0:16:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:04.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,戴  我一定戴  太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.95,0:16:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是为什么要做成白色翅膀形状的徽章呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.18,0:16:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,依文居然送我们礼物…真可疑…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,主人不愿意社团一直被称为「涅吉魔社（暂定）」才…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:19.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…总之主人就是不乐意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不干！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:25.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总体来说主人是模仿了Thousand Master的赤色羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而将它称为白色羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白色…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…羽翼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.96,0:16:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.87,0:16:35.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好啊  这名称不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.81,0:16:39.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀…怎么行…我总觉得呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.03,0:16:42.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,依文也挺懂得风雅的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.82,0:16:43.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对她刮目相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但那个徽章是社团成员的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以去英国之前弄丢了徽章的人将被强行劝退
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.72,0:16:52.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:57.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.56,0:17:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要夺走那个徽章  就能去英国旅行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.30,0:17:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是怎么办呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:04.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那两个人好像也进行过那啥特殊训练吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.41,0:17:07.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我看还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:09.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.64,0:17:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  先看我表现
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.95,0:17:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  那边的两位小姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的徽章很不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:23.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是刚好路过的徽章迷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:25.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,徽章仙士  徽章人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:28.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我很中意你们那徽章…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.63,0:17:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不想受伤的话就把东西交出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.40,0:17:37.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么啊  裕奈同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.08,0:17:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.11,0:17:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么露馅了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:41.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是夕映吉！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.07,0:17:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇～  不算  刚刚那个不算哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…你们就当作什么也发生过哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,噢噢！  两位的徽章都很可爱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.70,0:17:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么徽章来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.95,0:17:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能借我们看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.65,0:17:57.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这个是刚刚依文洁琳同学给的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:18:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  真是好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:01.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这徽章真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.12,0:18:03.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能借来看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:06.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  这可不能随便借…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:08.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥？  借一下而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.61,0:18:09.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.67,0:18:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是拿在手上看一下而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.79,0:18:15.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说…你们为什么突然对这种普普通通的徽章…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.08,0:18:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才不普通呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呜  好想拿在手里看一看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:23.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你看…就是这个白白的有点像翅膀的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.32,0:18:25.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好销魂啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.69,0:18:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:27.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:28.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.93,0:18:29.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莳绘同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.07,0:18:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～为什么啊  小夕映
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.81,0:18:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么嘛  夕映吉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么为什么啊  真是太可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.66,0:18:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们另有企图吧  裕奈同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.74,0:18:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管了！  逮住她们！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你们搞什么名堂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.42,0:18:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.36,0:18:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.00,0:18:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,两位真不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:18:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Practe Biginar
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:18:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Lux{\r}\N光芒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.98,0:19:03.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快逃  和香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:04.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.39,0:19:08.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊  既然你们不赏脸…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.85,0:19:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向敌人开炮！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.31,0:19:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:16.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.97,0:19:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.52,0:19:22.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Elementa Aerialia,Venti Apirantes{\r}\N大地的精灵  瞬息之风啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:25.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Cito Aeuntes Ac Inimicis Meis Me Defendant{\r}\N降临至此  保护吾等御于外敌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.07,0:19:27.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Limes Aerialis{\r}\N风阵结界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.04,0:19:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧！  居然弹开了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.83,0:19:32.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Practe Biginar
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.81,0:19:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Vente{\r}\N风啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.77,0:19:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夕映好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.21,0:19:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这难道就是特训成果吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.67,0:19:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  大家分头追
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,噢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.69,0:20:00.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夕映好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.31,0:20:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的跟魔法师一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  对裕奈同学她们用魔法真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:09.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她们的行动很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.03,0:20:12.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚拿到徽章立刻就发生这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这应该是依文洁琳同学对部内成员进行的考验
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.42,0:20:18.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很可能是一种考试
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.69,0:20:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果徽章被夺走…我们就会失去部内成员的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,0:20:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个想法应该没错吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.98,0:20:25.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可不能被她们抓住  和香  用你的道具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.51,0:20:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Diaria Ejus{\r}\N本我绘图日记
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.13,0:20:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Minora Quadrupla{\r}\N简易小型版4分册
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.81,0:20:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Adeant{\r}\N显现
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.66,0:20:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Tumcogitationes Vestigent De{\r}\N追踪思考
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.11,0:20:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Sasacie Macie{\r}\N佐佐木莳绘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Acasie Juna{\r}\N明石裕奈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.77,0:20:45.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Oocoutie Acira{\r}\N大和内晶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:47.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}et Izumie Acone{\r}\N和泉亚子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.13,0:20:50.39,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}7月27日  裕奈    呜～  太大意了  实在是出乎意料  但…但是还不能放弃！  就算是为了亚子也要拿到手  首先是兵分两路  西边…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.71,0:20:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来  就可以实时追踪四个人的思维了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.08,0:20:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是和香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.78,0:20:57.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就让我们来完美地逃脱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.64,0:20:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.11,0:21:04.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祭典很好玩呢  枫姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  确实不假呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.90,0:21:07.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.97,0:21:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.55,0:21:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,突击！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:14.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自爆了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:15.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.58,0:21:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  那里的小姐们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.54,0:21:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,徽章蛮不错的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.86,0:21:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.95,0:21:25.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖把东西给交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.87,0:21:26.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不然的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.15,0:21:28.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.23,0:21:30.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回去重练过再来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.94,0:21:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对不起  小姐们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:37.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,菲部长实在太强大了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.23,0:21:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.62,0:21:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说  那个肌肉大叔是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春春的男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.17,0:21:47.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夕映跟和香  哪里都找不到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.58,0:21:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  两个小鬼有两下子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.90,0:21:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊班长  我们失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.40,0:21:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能啦  不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.81,0:21:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:22:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看我亲自出马
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.35,0:22:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜同学～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来一决胜负！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.72,0:22:20.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,班…班长你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.84,0:22:24.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜同学…以前还基本跟我打平手的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.60,0:22:27.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候拉开了那么大的距离…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.69,0:22:29.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,班…班长？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.65,0:22:32.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  不能在这里放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.53,0:22:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要认真出手了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.53,0:22:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.77,0:22:39.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪广绫香流  合气柔术
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.81,0:22:43.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天地分断掌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.66,0:22:45.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.56,0:22:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉如何啊  明日菜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.65,0:22:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,班长拼尽全力也不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.02,0:22:56.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.03,0:22:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜同学和班长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.97,0:23:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本来一直当明日菜是武艺方面的劲敌…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.33,0:23:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事情…太耻辱了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.94,0:23:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.37,0:23:12.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我…有经过特训所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.60,0:23:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.53,0:23:16.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有破绽！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.25,0:23:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.17,0:23:21.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…搞什么啊  班长
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.93,0:23:23.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底想做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.80,0:23:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太狡猾了  太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.67,0:23:29.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜同学  笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.02,0:23:30.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩子脾气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.11,0:23:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩子脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.30,0:23:34.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,够了  快把那个徽章交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.95,0:23:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有了那个徽章  就能加入社团了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.01,0:23:37.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.02,0:23:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…原来如此啊  依文
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.88,0:23:42.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,苦恼吧  苦恼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.39,0:23:44.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.16,0:23:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对不起啊  班长
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.75,0:23:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个徽章实在…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.54,0:23:50.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.78,0:23:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,光你们去太不公平了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.72,0:23:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.36,0:23:57.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但…但是  那边搞不好会很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.50,0:23:58.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,危险？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.28,0:24:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会危险？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.34,0:24:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,需要特训才能应对的危险究竟是指什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.65,0:24:07.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让涅吉老师到那种地方去！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.08,0:24:09.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然你们也不准去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.93,0:24:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我作为班长…不批准
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.37,0:24:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真那么危险的话  去找警察之类的正规机构不是更好…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.23,0:24:19.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能这么简单倒好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.99,0:24:22.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂了  告诉你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.64,0:24:24.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞒着你们真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.77,0:24:27.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们非去不可
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.27,0:24:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果涅吉他不靠自己找到父亲的行踪  就没有任何意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.65,0:24:36.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲的事情他要不做个了结的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.83,0:24:38.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙就一步也迈不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.20,0:24:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也终于明白  他是那么一个麻烦的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.66,0:24:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们才决定帮他一把
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.65,0:24:53.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.42,0:24:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.20,0:24:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.27,0:25:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.91,0:25:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在说什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.63,0:25:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？啊…没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.65,0:25:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事啦  涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.25,0:25:11.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  涅吉弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.62,0:25:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去不去吃炒面？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.06,0:25:16.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,炒面吗？  好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.91,0:25:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜同学  我明白你们的决心了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.70,0:25:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？  班长你明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.99,0:25:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.18,0:25:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么重要的事情一直瞒着我  实在是不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.17,0:25:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回头要给我好好解释清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.96,0:25:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真糟糕～
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.60,0:25:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.74,0:25:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙  喊着来接人家现在却没半个人影
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.10,0:25:59.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么嘛…
